        <summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;For those of you who don&#x27;t know, (which is going to be most of you), I recently published my very first crate; &lt;a href=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;github.com&#x2F;bahdotsh&#x2F;zp&quot;&gt;zp&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;. &lt;code&gt;zp&lt;&#x2F;code&gt; is just a simple tool to copy contents from a file. I built zp so that I can learn rust properly. And by properly, I mean learning something and understanding it in a way I can use it to build cool&#x2F;useful things in the future.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;</summary>
        
